divs: Sighting DetailsNo other aircraft observed in the area, first 2 pair of red orbs moving very fast from se to nw, 2 more pairs one significantly behind the others heading same direction, then 1 single same speed same direction then 2 more pairs to follow, last single almost over the house. no flashing lights, dull red to dull orange orbs, lasted maybe 10 minutes, got a brief clip of 1 with cell phone camera. if they were aircraft, they were not ours.
Summary: observed at least 8 dull red orbs two pairs good separation, then consecutive pairs not following the same path but the same direction
